The body of the deceased was retrieved from the dam on Friday afternoon.The DP’s director of communication Emmanuel Tallam confirmed to the Nation that the deceased was a prison warden. An officer attached to Deputy President William Ruto’s communication team has committed suicide under unclear circumstances.
David Too, 51, is said to have plunged himself into Ngeria dam on Friday, an incident that caught family members and relatives by surprise.
According to family members, the deceased was attached to the DP’s security detail for several years.



